@startuml
title UC12 - Upload Lifecycle State
[*] --> Selected
Selected --> Validating : upload requested
Validating --> Rejected : invalid type/size
Validating --> Uploading : valid
Uploading --> Stored : storage success
Uploading --> Failed : storage error
Stored --> Linked : URL/path saved
Linked --> [*]
Rejected --> Selected : choose another file
Failed --> Selected : retry
@enduml
